### Enviar botões de resposta (até 3, sem misturar outros tipos)
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/sendButtons/{{instanceName}}
Content-Type: application/json
apikey: {{apiKey}}

{
  "number": "5599999999999",
  "title": "Escolha uma opção",
  "description": "Selecione abaixo:",
  "footer": "AtendAI",
  "buttons": [
    { "type": "reply", "id": "opt1", "displayText": "Opção 1" },
    { "type": "reply", "id": "opt2", "displayText": "Opção 2" },
    { "type": "reply", "id": "opt3", "displayText": "Opção 3" }
  ]
}

### Enviar botão de URL
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/sendButtons/{{instanceName}}
Content-Type: application/json
apikey: {{apiKey}}

{
  "number": "5599999999999",
  "title": "Acesse:",
  "buttons": [
    { "type": "url", "displayText": "Abrir site", "url": "https://example.com" }
  ]
}

### Enviar botão de chamada
POST {{baseUrl}}/message/sendButtons/{{instanceName}}
Content-Type: application/json
apikey: {{apiKey}}

{
  "number": "5599999999999",
  "title": "Contato",
  "buttons": [
    { "type": "call", "displayText": "Ligar", "phoneNumber": "+5511999999999" }
  ]
}

